A vintage 1960s-style illustration of a sleek film projector casting warm golden light onto a floating array of translucent tutorial cards and learning modules, arranged in a spiral pattern ascending upward. The scene has a retro corporate training aesthetic with muted orange, cream, and teal colors. Small silhouettes of office workers gather around the base, looking up in wonder at the illuminated knowledge cascade. The composition features halftone dot textures, rounded geometric shapes, and the optimistic mid-century modern design sensibility of old IBM promotional materials. Warm amber spotlights create dramatic shadows against a cream background.
